<h3>HTC Vive Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday 2023 Game Sales</h3>
<p>This year HTC is offering a<strong><a href="https://www.viveport.com/2023-black-friday"> 15% discount on monthly subscriptions or 20% discount on annual subscriptions</a></strong> to its Viveport Infinity game platform which offers unlimited access to a large library of PC VR and standalone games. The deal also includes permanent ownership of <em>The Break-In</em>, <em>RUINSMAGUS</em>, and <em>The Last Clockwinder</em> for those signing up for the annual subscription.</p>
